Text: Reminder HEF Launch PartyHi Jeffrey The launch party for the Houston Entrepreneurs Foundation is only week away The event is at Ruggles Enron Field in the late afternoonevening of November We expect it to be a fun event and hope that you will join us Below is a link where you can find out more details about the event and a form to RSVP moviehtml I did not see your name on the RSVP list and wanted to remind you to please RSVP if you plan to attend If you do not need additional information and would like to RSVP directly you can send an email to or call We look forward to seeing you on the th Regards Michelle Weisblatt and Billy Ladin Do You Yahoo Get your free yahoocom address at
